---
import Button from "@/components/Button.astro";
import SkillIcon from "@/components/SkillIcon.astro";
---

<section id="contact-me" class="contact-me">
  <article class="contact-me--section">
    <h2 class="contact-me--title">Skills</h2>
    <p>
      As a software developer, my technical expertise lies in a diverse range of
      tools, languages, and frameworks that enable me to bring digital solutions
      to life. Here are some of my key technical skills:
    </p>
    <div class="contact-me--skills">
      <SkillIcon icon="mdi:react" text="React" />
      <SkillIcon icon="mdi:react" text="React Native" />
      <SkillIcon icon="mdi:language-css3" text="CSS3" />
      <SkillIcon icon="mdi:language-javascript" text="JavaScript" />
      <SkillIcon icon="mdi:language-typescript" text="TypeScript" />
      <SkillIcon icon="mdi:language-html5" text="HTML5" />
      <SkillIcon icon="mdi:git" text="Git and Github" />
      <SkillIcon icon="mdi:tailwind" text="Tailwind CSS" />
    </div>
    <p>
      Beyond technical skills, effective software development relies on strong
      interpersonal abilities. Here are some of my key soft skills:
    </p>
    <div class="contact-me--skills">
      <SkillIcon icon="mdi:account-voice" text="English (C1)" />
      <SkillIcon icon="mdi:account-voice" text="Spanish (Native)" />
      <SkillIcon icon="mdi:search" text="Attention to detail" />
      <SkillIcon icon="mdi:people-group" text="Leadership" />
    </div>
  </article>
  <article class="contact-me--section">
    <h2 class="contact-me--title">Contact me</h2>
    <p>
      Have a question, a project in mind, or need a software developer? I'd love
      to hear from you! Feel free to reach out through my LinkedIn or my email:
    </p>
    <div class="contact-me--buttons">
      <Button
        onPress="https://www.linkedin.com/in/thebryanmartinez/"
        type="primary"
        text="Connect on LinkedIn"
      />
      <Button
        onPress="mailto:bryanmartz972@gmail.com"
        type="secondary"
        text="Send me an email"
      />
    </div>
    <p>
      I'm always eager to explore new opportunities and collaborate on exciting
      projects. Don't hesitate to reach outâ€”I'm looking forward to connecting
      with you! If you're interested in exploring more of my work, you can check
      my Github profile for a list of my projects.
    </p>

    <div class="contact-me--buttons">
      <Button
        onPress="https://github.com/thebryanmartinez"
        type="secondary"
        text="Explore my Github"
      />
    </div>
  </article>

  <style>
    .contact-me {
      display: flex;
      align-items: start;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 8rem;
      @media (max-width: 601px) {
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 4rem;
      }
    }

    .contact-me--section {
      display: grid;
      place-items: center;
      flex: 1;
    }

    .contact-me--title {
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }

    .contact-me--buttons {
      margin: 2rem 0rem;
      display: flex;
      gap: 1rem;

      @media (max-width: 1100px) {
        flex-direction: column;
      }
    }

    .contact-me--skills {
      display: grid;
      width: 100%;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
      grid-auto-flow: row;

      @media (max-width: 768px) {
        grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      }

      @media (max-width: 450px) {
        grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
      }
    }
  </style>
</section>
